{"tid":1652268,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【歷史撚】刺殺伊藤博文","createTime":"2019-10-13T15:29:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T15:36:02.000Z","uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"901ad61ff37a3af5dcc58ee1a100a1fc007192d8","tid":1652268,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:29:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">安重根</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1909年（明治四十二）10月26日上午九點半前後，安重根（1879&mdash;1910）在哈爾濱火車站站台上擊斃伊藤博文（1841&mdash;1909）。以命相搏的場面，卻有幾分戲劇色彩。在伊藤博文檢閱了俄軍儀仗隊，向前來迎接的各國領事館人員和當地日本居民致辭的時候，身穿西裝、頭戴鴨舌帽的安重根穿過俄國兵隊列，走到距離伊藤博文大約5米遠的地方，從容地掏出8連發勃朗寧手槍，打出了7發子彈。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 3發子彈命中伊藤博文</span></span>，其餘4發飛向伊藤身邊的人。<br />\n<br />\n大家要記住今日所付出嘅刺客義士嘅英名<br />\n民族英雄<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b09b46c3fd6c46101b3ba9649f2fd5eae510497","tid":1652268,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:31:34.000Z","msg":"民族英雄要謹記"},{"pid":"a512be42e5109bc5531f4f6292327c3577e2410b","tid":1652268,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:36:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}